<br>
And then I've been getting tells from other 55+ people asking if Horizons is recruiting.  I've been turning them away because I didn't think it'd be fair to recruit into a guild that wasn't doing anything lately.<br>
<br>
But it got me to wondering -- which of the established guilds ARE taking people?<br>
<br>
And I'm also wondering if I should open Horizons back up as a home for the approaching-60 crowd who want a guild but don't want to play 24/7.<br>
<br>
Post here if your guild is still somewhat open to new members -or- if you're also looking for a home.  (Or if you want, email me: wolfypaw@horizonsguild.org)<br>
<br>
